This paper is primarily focused on reinforcement learning, which falls under the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also discusses the use of predictions in a 3D navigation task, which could potentially fall under cs.CV (Computer Vision). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of regularization in the loss function, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.SY (Systems and Control). Finally, the paper discusses the use of value function predictions, which could fall under cs.RO (Robotics).
